data.description: Unique home just outside of town! The living room is inviting with wood beams running along the ceilings. A formal dining room and spacious kitchen awaits you! Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. Walk through your unheated bonus area onto the covered patio. The patio overlooks a fenced yard surrounded by mature trees! Another plus... no city taxes! Welcome home!
